        <p class="text-sm text-[#64748B]">Published <time datetime="2026-05-05">May 2026</time> &nbsp;·&nbsp; Updated <time datetime="2026-05-05" class="text-ink font-medium">May 2026</time></p>
      </div>
    </div>

